cu.explanation_en: Setting SCTP_INSTREAMS to -1 (negative value) will cause SCTP configuration errors and prevent F1 interface setup.

du.explanation_en: Setting ra_ContentionResolutionTimer to 10 (invalid value, valid range 0-7) will cause configuration validation failure and prevent RACH setup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 ra_ContentionResolutionTimer 設定為 10（無效值，有效範圍 0-7）會導致配置驗證失敗，並阻止 RACH 設定。
